  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe \u0b92\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc2\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "US will continue to cooperate to advance good governance - US Ambassador to President",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "US Ambassador to Sri Lanka Julie Chung said that the United States will continue to provide cooperation to Sri Lanka to advance good governance that respects human rights and listens to the aspirations of the people.",
        "He said this while meeting President Ranil Wickremesinghe at the President's Office today.",
        "During this we discussed how the political and economic crises in Sri Lanka have developed and how the two countries can travel together towards a brighter future.",
        "Our country and its people have been maintaining friendly relations with Sri Lanka for 70 years.",
        "Accordingly, the United States will continue to provide cooperation to advance good governance in Sri Lanka that respects human rights and listens to the aspirations of the people.' mentioned that.",
        "This is the second meeting with the US Ambassador since the inauguration of President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "It is worth noting that the US ambassador met President Ranil Wickremesinghe on the 22nd and discussed the attacks on the demonstrators."
      ],
